title: DOJ Fights Against Trump Special Master
itunes:title: DOJ Fights Against Trump Special Master
description: Yesterday, Biden's Department of Justice (DOJ) appealed federal Judge Aileen Cannon's ruling ordering a special master review of material seized by the FBI in the raid on President Trump's Mar-a-Lago residence. The DOJ is also seeking to resume their review of the documents seized - which they stopped at the judge's order. Jay, Jordan, and the Sekulow team discuss this and more today on Sekulow.
